Methodology

Bars per Session: 27 bars (6.5 hours Ã— 4 bars/hour)
Sample Size: 1,368 trading sessions
Analysis Period: August 2020 through January 2026

Calculation Methods:
â€¢ HOD/LOD Individual Percentages: Calculated as (frequency at bar / total sessions) Ã— 100
â€¢ Combined "HOD OR LOD" Probability: For each bar, counts sessions where EITHER extreme occurred at that bar or earlier. Handles overlapping cases where the same bar makes both HOD and LOD.

Definitions:
â€¢ HOD (High of Day): The highest price during RTH session
â€¢ LOD (Low of Day): The lowest price during RTH session
â€¢ Bar Number: Sequential 15-minute bar (Bar 1 = 09:30-09:45 ET)
â€¢ Percentage: (Frequency / 1,368 sessions) Ã— 100
â€¢ Cumulative %: Probability of seeing the extreme by that bar or earlier
